data.name: Natt, the Inestimable
data.notes: "Natt, the Inestimable" rarely makes an appearance in the same interior room as the probe light for FN Site 507 at the top of Slavebird Isle in Cauldros. Besides fast travelling over and over until the game loads Natt instead of the third Hellion Blatta it is also possible to fly back and forth outside at an angle that allows you to see when the Blatta despawn and respawn until the noticeable purple tyrant splotch appears.
